{"tid":1561260,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"多謝你地既努力 令我由暗黃變成鮮黃","createTime":"2019-09-11T14:02:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-11T14:16:34.000Z","uid":303719,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"e5ced2767c82268dfcf3eb814f065f56d668bc09","tid":1561260,"uid":303719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T14:02:04.000Z","msg":"話說我一路都黃底<br />\n不過好少表達出黎<br />\n每一晚都係對住電腦追返d news同post<br />\n哭過嬲過感動過<br />\n但咁耐以黎都只係出過兩次黎<br />\n一路都係自己一個人去遊行,去擺工<br />\n直到今日,誤打誤撞地巧遇中學生人鏈<br />\n見到D學生個個都好盡力叫口號,你地既表情你地既聲音我係唔會忘記<br />\n我今日終於儲夠經驗由暗黃變成鮮黃<br />\n黎緊我會出多D黎,同你地一齊爭取令香港變返我地認識既香港<br />\n<br />\n#親自fact checked, 人鏈係可以感染人<br />\n#和理非初哥 #遲來的激活<br />\n#感謝每一位勇武和理非<br />\n#不分化、不割蓆、不篤灰<br />\n#兄弟爬山 各自努力<br />\n#五大訴求 缺一不可<br />\n#香港人加油 萬事小心"},{"pid":"fc3f78e32ffec11ac87dd24ce03c46d87c68b458","tid":1561260,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T14:02:53.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPJ3iwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaPJ3iwW.png&h=bd74ec1d&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"d61c3504bc92eedfd6bede07e2c878ec2dc3f8ae","tid":1561260,"uid":56305,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T14:03:22.000Z","msg":"咁黎幫手啦<br />\n!<br />\n[多圖高清] [不廢up] 一人一文宣行動<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/dRzLwS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg